    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration experts! This vehicle is the perfect blank canvas for your next big project. While it definitely needs some mechanical attention and bodywork to get back to its best, it offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to build a car from the ground up or source quality components at a bargain price!",
